                    "3. Permafrost thaws in southern boreal — waterlogged conditions change to drier → increase in fire risk",
                    "4. Bark beetle outbreaks (e.g. mountain pine beetle) intensify — trees weakened by drought become vulnerable",
                    "5. Forest dieback in some areas shifts ecosystem from carbon sink to carbon source",
                    "6. Northward shift of boreal into tundra zone; southern boundary contracts as temperate species invade",
