                        occurs: "Mammalian muscle during intense exercise; red blood cells (no mitochondria)",
                        yield: "2 ATP per glucose",
                        fateLactate: "Lactate exported to liver → converted back to pyruvate → gluconeogenesis (Cori cycle)"
