                        executioners: "Caspase-3, -6, -7 — cleave cellular proteins",
                        substrates: ["PARP (poly-ADP ribose polymerase) — prevents DNA repair", "Lamins — nuclear disassembly", "Fodrin — cytoskeletal disruption", "CAD/ICAD — nuclease activation → DNA laddering"]
