                        NaK_ATPase: "Maintains gradients: 3 Na⁺ out / 2 K⁺ in per ATP; electrogenic (net negative charge inside)",
                        restingConductance: "At rest: higher K⁺ permeability (leak channels) → K⁺ diffuses out → inside negative"
