                            function: "Extrudes H⁺ using Na⁺ gradient → intracellular alkalinisation; Na⁺ and HCO₃⁻ reabsorption in kidney",
                            clinical: "Tenapanor (NHE3 inhibitor) — reduces intestinal Na⁺/phosphate absorption in CKD"
