                        nuclei: "Single nucleus per cell, centrally located",
                        control: "Involuntary (autonomic nervous system, hormones, local factors, stretch)",
                        specialFeatures: "Slow, sustained contractions; resistant to fatigue; can be stretched significantly and still contract effectively",
