                        characteristics: ["Fastest contraction speed", "Low mitochondria", "Low myoglobin (pale/white colour)", "Large diameter", "Fatigue quickly", "Highest force output"],
                        energySource: "Anaerobic glycolysis; glycogen → lactate",
                        adaptation: "Power and speed activities — sprinting, throwing, weightlifting",
