                    "2. Stomach: acidic pH inactivates amylase; no carbohydrate digestion",
                    "3. Duodenum: pancreatic amylase resumes → maltose, maltotriose",
                    "4. Brush border: maltase → glucose + glucose",
                    "5. Jejunum enterocytes: glucose absorbed via SGLT1 (Na⁺ cotransport)",
                    "6. Basolateral exit: GLUT2 → blood capillary",
