                    "2. CCK travels in blood to stomach",
                    "3. CCK inhibits gastric motility → pyloric sphincter tightens",
                    "4. Simultaneously triggers gallbladder contraction → bile released",
                    "5. And stimulates pancreatic enzyme secretion",
                    "6. Purpose: ensure fat is properly emulsified and digested before more fat arrives"
